    "As an appraiser, De la Faille himself had been misled by Wacker and had to admit his mistakes.": [],
    "He then published a supplement to his catalog in which he made the necessary corrections.": [],
    "This case, however, required a more systematic and comprehensive study on Van Gogh falsifications.": [],
